<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Chim loin ka um kho lo, rello in ka um kho lo
 Thiangthlarau rian ttuannak, ka chungah
 Mei bangin a ka kangh i, dai tein ka um kholo
 Van lei thuh mi Mana ka hmu cang e.

[C1]
   Eden kutka, dawh an hung cang
   Phunkip holhkip, kan za leng e
   Pathian pakhat, zumhnak pakhat
   Baptistma pakhat, cotu kan si.

[V2]
 Kan rawl tak cu Jesuh Khrih, a thisen le a taksa
 Ei le dingtu kan si, thlarau rawl
 Jerusalem a herh lo, Kerezim kan ngai tilo
 Kan taksa pumpi cu, Pathian biak inn.

[V3]
 Kan lanhtak puai tuufano, sual chungin kan za lennak
 Thihnak tei tho thanmi, a kan hruaitu
 A dongh tiang a kan hruai lai, A orh lei a kut nem in
 Van Kanaan kan phan lai, mithiang len nak.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>CHIM LO IN KA UM KHO LO</title>
</song>